      <data key="d8">PATIENT ROOM</data>
      <data key="d9">APPLIED_TO</data>
      <data key="d10">The ventilation system design is implemented and evaluated within the patient room environment, where airflow configuration affects contaminant transport from source to exhaust.</data>
