      <data key="d7">VENTILATION SYSTEM DESIGN</data>
      <data key="d8">INFECTION RISK</data>
      <data key="d9">REDUCES</data>
      <data key="d10">When ventilation design conforms to the hypothesized path principle and maintains an uninterrupted path from contaminant source to exhaust, it improves contaminant control and reduces infection risk.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.9</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">3fc1e87d-c54a-447e-9229-2850cf6a1b9b_chunk_3</data>
      <data key="d14">3fc1e87d-c54a-447e-9229-2850cf6a1b9b</data>
