      <data key="d8">92% REDUCTION IN AVERAGE INFECTION RISK</data>
      <data key="d9">REDUCES</data>
      <data key="d10">In the moving bus, opening windows reduced average infection risk by 92% compared with windows closed.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.99</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">e45568c3-e22e-4830-92f5-64de955e8aee_chunk_2</data>
      <data key="d14">e45568c3-e22e-4830-92f5-64de955e8aee</data>
