      <data key="d8">SARS-COV-2</data>
      <data key="d9">TARGETS</data>
      <data key="d10">Equipping the AC unit with an appropriate filter is proposed to reduce SARS-CoV-2 transmission risk by trapping particles. | The text explicitly states that infection risk can be reduced by equipping the AC unit with an appropriate filter.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.85</data>
