      <data key="d8">SARS-COV-2</data>
      <data key="d9">TARGETS</data>
      <data key="d10">The AC prefilter may reduce transport of virus-containing particles and thereby indirectly target SARS-CoV-2 transmission.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.73</data>
