      <data key="d8">PARTICLE SPREAD RATE ABOUT HALF OF CO2 WITH AC ON</data>
      <data key="d9">HAS_DOSE</data>
      <data key="d10">The observed lower particle spread rate with AC on is attributed to trapping by the AC prefilter.</data>
